name: Warmup_Div02_Sub02
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD2S2.CPF,
GmailD2S2.NOME,
GmailD2S2.EMAIL,
GmailD2S2.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S2.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD2S2.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD2S2.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S2.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV02_SUB02 GmailD2S2
